  ('828148a9-ab5c-432c-a6d4-2381d97862fc', 'LA.4.R.UT.3', 'Ask and answer questions: who, what, where, when, why, how to demonstrate understanding of key details in text.', 'language-arts', '4', 'Reading and Viewing', 'R', 'Use of Technology', 'UT', NULL, '3-4', 3, '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00', '2026-01-03T13:23:37.075008+00:00'),
